Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾德拉姆入港準備 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊旗艦阿馬迪厄斯來電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令官 您終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報敵艦接近…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬迪厄斯完成補給後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 艾倫格雷亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這艘船上執行艦隊指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以參謀長身份登艦後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號即是艦隊旗艦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…那艘船？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們旨在佔領地球圈的重要生產衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其與移動要塞達烏內斯強行對接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為攻略地球的前線基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用諾德拉姆內的工業生產能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我軍補給機能大幅提高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 衛星居民既可作為勞動力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人將無法輕易向我們發動進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！這種作戰的成功可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是伊澤爾坎特大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回我們的故鄉地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的時刻到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重申一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰 以天神號為旗艦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與艾倫格雷亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖坐鎮艦橋指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還須天神號艦長協助司令部運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾絲中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近處看上去還真俊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 各艦來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦隊 開始出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前線更易作出精確指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這場戰鬥結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要返回火星圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內人不曾冰眠 時光蹉跎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共度最後的時光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難為你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們告訴我作戰部署
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是預備隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不安排我去最前線？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 德西爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保後備兵源是戰術之本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防萬一 命令你待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不幹！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對菲利特·明日野 你有特殊的感情在作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣上戰場…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要崩了菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 我活到今天的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再放任他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何做？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會考慮處分的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵人艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 是擊退那些人類公敵的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 開始佈陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環形陣列 準備啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為電磁終端輸入坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍最新武器 光子環形陣列是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是將電磁終端呈圓環狀排列在宇宙空間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令電子在內側旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出強大的動能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用天神號的光子爆破炮完成指向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如何不被敵人察覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環充電完成前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得讓敵人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員到齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我們要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為此需要做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥到最後的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論對手是誰 都要戰鬥到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥雖苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是失去戰友會更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住了嗎 要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 一定活著要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船是我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許不合時宜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次…關於求婚的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果不嫌棄我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發咯 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達AGE-2 巴雷特雙槍 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Bouncer 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊 奧布萊特·洛倫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Genoace-2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克斯·哈特維 Adele-1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎·甘海爾 Adele-2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的作戰太蠻幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您必須三思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒 想想我們家鄉的慘狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便以生命為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要實現伊澤爾坎特大人理想中的伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的未來 只存在於伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這雙手打開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往未來的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁終端 部署完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 電子加速開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電子加速程序開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 天神號沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 巴雷特雙槍的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那個X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 這高達不是菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不膩味也難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二戰隊 追擊敵機動戰士隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游擊部隊投入作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怪陣是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫使我方集中兵力 引誘我們中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩挲副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓達烏內斯緊急調頭 朝向坐標F21方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 機動戰士隊正準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令他們停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進系統應急模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍已經完成了那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…這麼快？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急通知全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止追擊敵人 立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 好不容易突破陣線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環形陣列
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射環確認形成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入最終程序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 準備指向射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍 撤離光子陣列射線軸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人戰線後方 偵測到強力光子輻射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癸干忒斯之盾 系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指向射擊 準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 指向發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未發現重大損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電子光束遭到擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵要塞沒有受損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人似乎部署了某種干涉掩體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然當場化解了我們的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的聯邦 藏著那種武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以司令官下令暫時撤退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:14:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體…不聽使喚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙我對付得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿莉莎她們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 快去救隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和沒事…有點差距
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長 我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從外面幫你打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 亞瑟姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 你是個盡讓人操心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我如果做得更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出 你是個厲害的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是X-Rounder 也夠厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個超級機師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個天下無敵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我厲害得多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙第一的機師…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫少校的G-Bouncer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號…消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 沃爾夫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人從我的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 迄今為止多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提多盡興了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當救世主的豪言壯語 要兌現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾絲艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環陣列的狀態如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環陣列再充填 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你 絕不放過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲法和涅特的識別信號消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 他們死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為他們報仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標 F28宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 不許靠近那片宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲法和涅特是被德西爾操縱才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的話你們也會步他們的後塵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那裏還有高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在的實力無法估量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子不是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預…預判不出 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是X-Rounder！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級機師…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有輸的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輸的道理！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對親哥哥也見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一開始就是這麼打算的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意言辭 多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要成為障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓會不擇手段抵達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現伊澤爾坎特大人夢想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人為什麼絲毫沒有攻擊諾德拉姆的跡象？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令全軍向敵移動要塞發起總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括諾德拉姆守軍在內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部兵力投入作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的目的不是毀滅衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾倫格雷亞斯 這裏拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們的生命即將燃盡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色要塞欲玉石俱焚 向地球墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那赤紅的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官負責指揮和最終決策
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企劃作戰 輔佐司令官是參謀員的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾倫格雷亞斯先生對父親來說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可或缺的存在

